description: Includes all the necessary components to replace worn or damaged WhisperLite™,  WhisperLite Universal, or WhisperLite International stoves and pump parts. Comes with instructions and durable carrying case.Jet and cable tool.O-rings and sizing chart – to let you know which one goes where.Priming wick.Pump cup oil.Safety pin.Pump seal.Air tube.Fuel tube bushing.Check valve plug.Pump cup.Shaker needle (with cover).Check valve ball.Check valve spring.WhisperLite G jet (no mark).WhisperLite International G jet.WhisperLite International K jet.Jet cleaning wire.Check valve assembly.Fuel tube and filter.
name: MSR WL/WLI/WLU Expedition Service Kit
